title: Surviving Your Adolescents by Thomas W. Phelan
description:
Surviving Your Adolescents: How to Manage-And Let Go Of-Your 13-18 Year Olds by Thomas W. Phelan PhD


Living with a teenager is no picnic. There are times when you must bite your tongue as they push towards independence. 

Or, if you sense there is trouble, there are times when you must take charge. This program gives parents a step-by-step approach that will help end the hassles and offer concrete solutions.

Genre: Nonfiction | Educational
